    <title>Jacob Wohl is running an AI lobbying company under a pseudonym, Politico reports</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="An image of Jack Burkman and Jacob Wohl against a radioactive background" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/o02Xh_impifMoU5r2lMq_PxKE78=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73559457/acastro_illo_226067_0002.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Image: Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="vjXoIf"&gt;Jacob Wohl and Jack Burkman are &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2022/7/22/23273280/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-predator-dc-film-shoot-assault-allegations-payment"&gt;far-right activists&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2022/12/01/1140096697/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-robocalls-ohio-sentence"&gt;convicted felons&lt;/a&gt;, and engineers of &lt;a href="https://www.cnn.com/2018/10/31/media/gateway-pundit-robert-mueller-false-allegations/index.html"&gt;questionable political stunts&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;em&gt;Politico&lt;/em&gt; reports that &lt;a href="https://www.politico.com/news/2024/09/02/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-ai-lobbying-pseudonyms-00176917"&gt;they are now also running LobbyMatic&lt;/a&gt;, a company that sells an “&lt;a href="https://www.lobbymatic.com/"&gt;AI automation platform for lobbyists&lt;/a&gt;.”  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="Yy5Fi2"&gt;LobbyMatic claims on its website that its AI-powered software can do everything — like automatically monitor congressional hearings or “supercharge research” into legislative and regulatory issues. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="c-float-left c-float-hang"&gt;&lt;aside id="RlJ2CP"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="readmore" data-anthem-component-data='{"stories":[{"title":"Conservative activist Jacob Wohl charged with running election robocall scheme ","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2020/10/1/21497823/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-michigan-robocall-voter-intimidation-felony-charges"},{"title":"Conservative pranksters face $5 million proposed fine over robocalls ","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2021/8/24/22640239/fcc-jacob-wohl-burkman-election-robocalls-fine"},{"title":"Crew members on Jacob Wohl’s Predator DC report assaults during filming ","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2022/7/22/23273280/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-predator-dc-film-shoot-assault-allegations-payment"}]}'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/aside&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="rmIC0H"&gt;Jumping on the AI hypewagon is a perfectly respectable career move. The problem is that sources have told &lt;em&gt;Politico &lt;/em&gt;that Wohl and Burkman are running the firm under the pseudonyms Jay Klein and Bill Sanders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="x75LuB"&gt;LobbyMatic has no leadership listed on its official website. A company by the name of...&lt;/p&gt;
